1140
00:57:02,090 --> 00:57:03,170
Take your baby.

1141
00:57:06,130 --> 00:57:07,570
This isn't what we wanted, Bhanu.

1142
00:57:23,690 --> 00:57:28,010
I'll find you a place in Juhu,
