00:58:04,850 --> 00:58:05,690
What's wrong?

1164
00:58:06,290 --> 00:58:07,450
Why this sad face?

1165
00:58:08,330 --> 00:58:09,410
What happened?

1166
00:58:14,850 --> 00:58:17,410
