I am nowhere close to your age.

1234
01:03:44,450 --> 01:03:45,490
I am just 38 years old.

1235
01:03:45,570 --> 01:03:47,410
How can he be Mimi's husband?

1236
01:03:47,490 --> 01:03:48,530
